I'm gonna miss you, you know.

34
00:03:10,896 --> 00:03:15,300
- Any outgoing?
- Just... This.

35
00:03:15,367 --> 00:03:18,069
Don't post it. It's for you.

36
00:03:18,137 --> 00:03:20,505
It's been discussed among the partners

37
00:03:20,573 --> 00:03:22,107
that you be promoted

38
00:03:22,174 --> 00:03:24,642
to Director of Agency Operations.

39
00:03:25,978 --> 00:03:27,445
My goodness.

40
00:03:27,513 --> 00:03:29,914
Now it's a dreadful reality

41
